name: Rotten Eggz Fight: 5v5 Shooter
description:
Like TPS games? We got you covered. Enjoy Third Person Shooting Game like never before. You can be anything you want. Wanna be an egg or vegetables maybe?You can!

Enjoy the new aspect of TPS shooting game where humans doesn't exist anymore. You are on a planet where vegetables,eggs etc rule. So what are you waiting for. Download now & start enjoying the most diversified Third Person Shooting Game of 2018.

Features:

• Choose From A Wide Variety Of Shooter Options
• A TPS With Amazing Graphics
• Smooth Controls
• Real Physics Movements
• Something Fun And Exciting
• Wide Sea Port Environment To Move About.
